{"id":111,"ayahs":[{"number":18,"arabic":"وَقَالَتِ ٱلْيَهُودُ وَٱلنَّصَٰرَىٰ نَحْنُ أَبْنَٰٓؤُا۟ ٱللَّهِ وَأَحِبَّٰٓؤُهُۥ ۚ قُلْ فَلِمَ يُعَذِّبُكُم بِذُنُوبِكُم ۖ بَلْ أَنتُم بَشَرٌۭ مِّمَّنْ خَلَقَ ۚ يَغْفِرُ لِمَن يَشَآءُ وَيُعَذِّبُ مَن يَشَآءُ ۚ وَلِلَّهِ مُلْكُ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضِ وَمَا بَيْنَهُمَا ۖ وَإِلَيْهِ ٱلْمَصِيرُ","translation":"And [both] the Jews and the Christians say, \"We are God's children, and His beloved ones.\" Say: \"Why, then, does He cause you to suffer for your sins? Nay, you are but human beings of His creating. He forgives whom He wills, and He causes to suffer whom He wills: for God's is the dominion over the heavens and the earth and all that is between them, and with Him is all journeys' end.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/687.mp3","surahId":5,"words":[{"id":20702,"position":1,"arabic":"وَقَالَتِ","translation":"এবং বলে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_018_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":20703,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْيَهُودُ","translation":"ইয়াহুদীরা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_018_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":20704,"position":3,"arabic":"وَٱلنَّصَـٰرَىٰ","translation":"ও খ্রিষ্টানরা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_018_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":20705,"position":4,"arabic":"نَحْنُ","translation":"\"আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_018_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":20706,"position":5,"arabic":"أَبْنَـٰٓؤُا۟","translation":"সন্তানগণ","audioUrl":"wbw/005_018_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":20707,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/005_018_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":20708,"position":7,"arabic":"وَأَحِبَّـٰٓؤُهُۥ ۚ","translation":"ও প্রিয় পাত্র তাঁর\"","audioUrl":"wbw/005_018_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":20710,"position":8,"arabic":"قُلْ","translation":"বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/005_018_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":20711,"position":9,"arabic":"فَلِمَ","translation":"\"তবে কেন (আল্লাহ)","audioUrl":"wbw/005_018_010.mp3","charTypeN